>>1a28990a-8e10-40e4-a124-be75b56973f0
There's no need to actually right click and save. All the stuff is already saved in your zeronet folder. Just download them with [seed] or by expanding them, then you just have to copy them to another folder from the data/users folder.
If you're running Linux, you can make a folder called 08chan_files in your zeronet folder, and then do this:
[code]
find ./common/data/1DdPHedr5Tz55EtQWxqvsbEXPdc4uCVi9D/data/users/*/src | while read i ; do cp $i ./08chan_files ; done[/code]
which will copy all the files you've already downloaded into one folder.
